00:00:33,080 --> 00:00:36,620
DALEK 1: <i>The humans have been told to begin the test.</i>
已经通知人类开始实验

8
00:00:36,820 --> 00:00:40,120
DALKE 2: <i>Any delay will result in death.</i>
任何人拖延都将被处死

9
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:42,840
DALEK 2: <i>There will be no delay!</i>
不允许有拖延!

10
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:47,720
- WATERFIELD: Mollie, Mollie.
- MAXTIBLE: Mr. McCrimmon has been kidnapped!
Mollie, Mollie. McCrimmon先生被绑架了!

11
00:00:47,940 --> 00:00:51,180
- MAXTIBLE: It means the end of us.
- WATERFIELD:  Unless we can find him quickly.
- 这意味着我们完蛋了  - 除非我们能赶紧找到他

12
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:54,020
- DOCTOR: Straw.   - WATERFIELD: I beg your pardon?
- 稻草  - 你说什么?

13
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,650
DOCTOR: A piece of straw.
一小截稻草

14
00:01:02,180 --> 00:01:04,540
TOBY: Had a cosy little sleep, young swell?
小觉睡的还舒服吧, 年轻人?

15
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:10,060
TOBY: Lively, is it? Maybe you'd like to sleep again?
醒了吧, 对不? 是不是还想睡一觉?

16
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:13,820
TOBY: I've got Mr. Nod here. He'll have you snorin' as good as ever.
我这里有位“点头”先生, 他会让你的呼噜震天响的

17
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,550
JAMIE: What do you want?
你想要怎么样?

18
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:17,840
TOBY: I'm to be well paid. Have no fear of that.
我会得到很好的报酬, 我不怕那个

19
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:20,590
JAMIE: Oh, and for what? I don't know you.
哦, 得到什么报酬?  我不认识你

20
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:24,720
TOBY: This your man, sir?
这是你要的人, 先生?

21
00:01:24,900 --> 00:01:27,440
TERRALL: Toby! What in Hades have you done?
Toby! 你到底干了什么?

22
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:30,580
TOBY: Why, I brought 'im from the house, like you said.
怎么了, 我把他从房子里带过来了啊, 正如你说的

23
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,510
TERRALL: I said nothing of the kind.
我可没说这样的话

24
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:34,600
TOBY: Well ya did, sir! Honest ya did.
你说过, 先生! 你真的说过

25
00:01:34,740 --> 00:01:36,760
TOBY: A guinea ya promised me.
许诺给我一几尼呢

26
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:41,060
TOBY: I done what ya said. You don't get outta payin'.
我已经做了你要求的, 你别想不付钱

27
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:43,440
TERRALL: Be careful how you speak to me, Toby!
注意你跟我说话的方式, Toby!

28
00:01:45,300 --> 00:01:47,880
TERRALL: There's your money. Get out!
这是给你的钱, 出去!

29
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,140
TERRALL: Where's Toby?
Toby 哪儿去了?

30
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:06,300
JAMIE: You just sent him about his business.
你刚把他打发走了啊

31
00:02:06,580 --> 00:02:08,500
JAMIE: Look, what's the matter? Are you all right?
嘿, 这怎么回事? 你没事吧?

32
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,640
TERRALL: Where's Victoria Waterfield?
Victoria Waterfield 在哪儿?

33
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:11,900
JAMIE: I don't know.
我不知道

34
00:02:12,250 --> 00:02:14,760
- TERRALL: Yes, you do.
- JAMIE: I tell you, I don't even know her!
- 你知道  - 我跟你说, 我都不认识她

35
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:18,520
TERRALL: You're in the house, a friend of Maxtible's.
You must know!
你在这个房子里, 你是 Maxtible 的朋友, 你肯定知道!

36
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,280
JAMIE: No, listen, I'm telling...
不, 听着, 我说的是...

37
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:28,340
TERRALL: Ha, I must apologize for that villain Toby.
哈, 我必须为那个恶棍 Toby 的事向你道歉

38
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:31,200
TERRALL: He was telling lies, of course.
I shall escort you to the house.
当然, 他说的都是谎言. 我护送你回房子里去

39
00:02:31,260 --> 00:02:33,400
JAMIE: Uh, You.... you just asked me about Victoria Waterfield.
哦, 你...你刚才还在问我 Victoria Waterfield 的事情

40
00:02:33,670 --> 00:02:35,140
TERRALL: Oh, she's in Paris.
噢, 她还在巴黎呢

41
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:38,320
TERRALL: I'm afraid I haven't introduced myself - Arthur Terrall.
恐怕我还没有介绍我自己 - Arthur Terrall

42
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,120
JAMIE: Well, never mind about that.  Did you or did you not...
哦, 先别说这个. 你有还是没有...

43
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:43,280
JAMIE: ask that man to knock me on the head and bring me in here?
...叫那个人把我打晕, 再把我带到这里来?

44
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:45,220
TERRALL: I, oh...certainly not!
我...当然没有啊

45
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:47,320
JAMIE: Doctor
博士

46
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:51,660
TERRALL: Oh. I see you're in good hands now.
I won't detain you any further.
哦, 我看你现在碰到朋友了. 我就不再耽误你了. 

47
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:54,140
- TERRALL: Good day, Doctor.   - DOCTOR: Oh, good day to you.
- 日安, 博士  - 哦, 你也日安

48
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:57,070
JAMIE: He's mad. Stark, staring mad!
他疯了, 他完全疯了

49
00:02:57,330 --> 00:02:58,520
DOCTOR: Yes, I know. I was listening.
是的, 我知道, 刚才我听到了

50
00:02:58,580 --> 00:03:00,540
- DOCTOR: Let's have a look at that head of yours. Come along.
- JAMIE: Look, it's all right, Doctor.
- 我们来看看你的头吧, 过来  - 哦, 没事的, 博士

51
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:03,240
JAMIE: One minute he says this,
the next minute he says that.
前一分钟他在说这个, 后一分钟他又说那个

52
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:04,660
JAMIE: Can you make it out, Doctor?
你能搞明白吗, 博士?

53
00:03:04,780 --> 00:03:06,660
JAMIE: I'm knocked on the head and I'm brought in here.
我被人敲晕了脑袋, 带到了这里

54
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:10,160
JAMIE: Then that man Terrall enters
and denies having ordered the other man to do it.
那个Terrall 进来这里, 又否认是他让那个人干的

55
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:13,360
JAMIE: Well, then he changes, and starts
asking about Victoria Waterfield
然后, 他又变了, 开始问 Victoria Waterfield 的事情,

56
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:16,420
JAMIE: And in the next breath, he tells me she's in Paris!
下一秒钟他又告诉我她在巴黎!

57
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:18,420
DOCTOR: I know what's happened to Victoria.
我知道 Victoria 发生了什么事

58
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,590
JAMIE: What has?
什么事?

59
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:21,680
DOCTOR: She's a prisoner of the Daleks.
她成了 Daleks 的囚徒

60
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,880
DALEK: <i>Hurry!</i>
快点!

61
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,640
VICTORIA: Why am I being moved?
为什么要转移我?

62
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:38,080
VICTORIA: Are you taking me back to my father?
你们要带我回到我父亲那里吗?

63
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:41,920
DALEK: <i>No, you are being moved. </i>
不, 是给你换个地方

64
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:49,280
DALEK: Pick up your cover.
带上你的外套

65
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,120
DALEK: Follow.
跟上

66
00:03:55,700 --> 00:04:01,020
DALEK: Do not be afraid. You are not to be exterminated.
不用害怕, 你不会被终结掉

67
00:04:11,380 --> 00:04:13,620
DALEK: Do not delay.
不要磨蹭

68
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,920
DALEK: Move.
走

69
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,220
WATERFIELD: You've warned him - told him about the Daleks?
你警告他了, 把 Daleks 的事情告诉他了?

70
00:04:40,340 --> 00:04:42,460
- DOCTOR: Yes, of course I did!
- WATERFIELD: But you were expressly told...
- 是的, 我当然干了  - 但你被明令禁止...

71
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,240
DOCTOR: Oh, fiddlesticks! Bosh!
哦, 胡说! 放屁!

72
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:47,740
DOCTOR: Jamie will cooperate. You may be certain of that.
Jamie 会合作的. 这个事情你可以放心

73
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:50,600
- WATERFIELD: Are you sure?   - DOCTOR: Yes, certainly sure.
- 你确定吗?   - 是的, 当然确定

74
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,540
DOCTOR: Jamie will do everything he is asked to do.
让 Jamie 做任何事情, 他都会去做

75
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:56,120
JAMIE: Now come along, we must go and find Maxtible.
来吧, 我们得去找 Maxtible 了

76
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:18,800
DALEK: The female human being has been moved.
那个人类女性已经被转移

77
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:21,040
MAXTIBLE: Everything is prepared.
一切已经准备就绪

78
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:24,000
DALEK: The testing equipment is ready?
实验设备准备好了吗?

79
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:28,500
MAXTIBLE: I think you will be pleased with the man,
I've had specially brought from London.
我想你们会满意这个人, 我特意从伦敦带过来的

80
00:05:28,980 --> 00:05:31,720
- MAXTIBLE: Ah, he works in my house.   - DALEK: Show me!
- 他在我房子里做事  - 给我看

81
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:40,420
MAXTIBLE: You will understand that he is rather simple.
你要明白他是一个相当简单的人

82
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:45,900
MAXTIBLE: He's quite dumb, but, uh... that has its advantages for us.
他很笨, 不过...对我们而言这有他的优势

83
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:49,220
MAXTIBLE: His mind is, how shall I say, undeveloped.
他的大脑, 怎么说呢, 不太发达

84
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,900
MAXTIBLE: He will not understand you, the Daleks.
他搞不懂你们 Daleks

85
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,820
- MAXTIBLE: Uh, I mean he will be terrified of you.   - DALEK: Show me!
- 我是说, 他是会害怕你们  - 给我看

86
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,080
MAXTIBLE: Ohh, I beg your pardon, uh...
哦, 我很抱歉

87
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,260
MAXTIBLE: Kemel!
Kemel!​

88
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,740
MAXTIBLE: Will you come with me?
你跟我来

89
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,280
MAXTIBLE: I want you to stand here.
我要你站在这里

90
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:28,100
MAXTIBLE: No, no, no, no, no, face the cabinet. Good.
不, 不, 不, 面朝柜子. 好了

91
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:35,640
MAXTIBLE: Now, bend that.
现在, 掰弯那个

92
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:24,160
MAXTIBLE: Excellent Kemel, excellent.
很好, Kemel, 很好

93
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:28,280
Now, you'll help me with these stools.
现在, 帮我摆一下这几个凳子

94
00:07:45,180 --> 00:07:50,220
MAXTIBLE: Now, Kemel. One blow. Break the plank!
现在, Kemel, 一次, 打断这块木头!

95
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:03,220
MAXTIBLE: Very good Kemel. I'm very pleased with you.
很好, Kemel, 我对你很满意

96
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:07,840
MAXTIBLE: Now you can put on your jacket. Come over here.
现在你可以穿上你的夹克了. 到这里来

97
00:08:12,220 --> 00:08:17,200
MAXTIBLE: Now, I want you to listen carefully. See this man?
现在, 我想要你听仔细了, 看到这个人了吗?

98
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:22,490
MAXTIBLE: Now, I'm going to take you to a place that I want you to guard,
现在, 我要带你去一个地方, 期望你做好守卫工作

99
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:25,300
MAXTIBLE: and this young man will try and get past you
而这个年轻人会试图越过你

100
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:27,220
and you are not to let him. Do you understand?
你不能允许他过去, 你明白吗?

101
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,840
MAXTIBLE: Oh, he's an evil villain, Kemel
哦, 他是一个邪恶的坏人, Kemel,

102
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:35,040
a cutthroat who would gladly murder us all in our beds, if he could.
他会残忍地将我们所有人杀死在床上, 如果他得到机会

103
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:38,020
MAXTIBLE: You will remember this man, hmm?
你要记住这个人, 嗯?

104
00:08:39,690 --> 00:08:42,690
MAXTIBLE: Right. Well, you come with me and I will direct you.
好了, 你跟我来, 我带你去

105
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:04,900
MAXTIBLE: This is the entrance to the south wing of my house,
这里是我房子的南厢入口

106
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:10,240
MAXTIBLE: and through here will pass
the man I showed you in the picture.
图片里面那个人就会从这里过来

107
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:14,640
MAXTIBLE: The door itself is an obstacle.
这门就是一个屏障

108
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,680
MAXTIBLE: No, no, wait!
不, 不, 等等!

109
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:35,300
MAXTIBLE: Now, if he gets through here, you will deal with him.
现在, 如果他到这里来, 你要对付他

110
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:37,700
Go now.
去吧

111
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,880
DALEK: We do not trust you.
我们不信任你

112
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,300
DOCTOR: Then we're quits, aren't we?
那我们退出, 可以吗?

113
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:56,140
DALEK: But we have your time machine.
但你的时间机器在我们手上

114
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:58,200
DALEK: So, you will obey us.
所以, 你要服从我们

115
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:07,120
DOCTOR: They want the "Human Factor", is that right?
他们想要“人类特质”, 对吗?

116
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:09,000
WATERFIELD: Yes, that is what they want.
是的, 那就是他们想要的

117
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,620
DOCTOR: Very complex.
这很复杂

118
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:16,880
And you want to introduce
this "human factor" into the race of Daleks?
. 你们期望把“人类特质”加入到 Daleks 种族中去?

119
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:21,860
DALEK: Yes, the conquest of humanity has eluded us.
是的, 人类的征服能力让我们很困惑

120
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:24,780
DALEK: The Daleks must know why.
Daleks 必须明白为什么

121
00:10:25,020 --> 00:10:27,170
DOCTOR: But, why choose Jamie for this test?
但是, 为什么挑选 Jamie 做这个实验?

122
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:30,320
DALEK: His travelling with you makes him unique.
他跟你一起旅行, 这让他变得独特

123
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:31,560
DOCTOR: But why him? Why not me?
但为什么是他, 为什么不是我?

124
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:33,100
- DALEK: Request denied.   - DOCTOR: Why?
- 拒绝回答  - 为什么?

125
00:10:33,380 --> 00:10:38,780
DALEK: You have travelled too much through time.
You are more than human.
你在时间中旅行得太久了, 你不仅仅是个人类了

126
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:40,880
DOCTOR: I see.
我明白了

127
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:44,320
DOCTOR: What is this?
这是什么?

128
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:47,940
MAXTIBLE: They have been brought from the Dalek planet.
他们是从 Dalek 星球带过来的

129
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:50,200
- DOCTOR: Skaro!   - DALEK: Yes.
- Skaro<i>(注: Daleks 的母星)</i>  - 是的

130
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:55,650
DALEK: Their life force is dormant.
Before it is activated, we want...
他们目前处于休眠状态, 激活之前, 我们想...

131
00:10:55,780 --> 00:10:59,200
DOCTOR: You want the "human factor" introduced. I see.
你们想要引入“人类特质”, 我知道了

132
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,820
DALEK: You will obey us!
你要服从我们!

133
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:02,120
DOCTOR: I will make up my own mind!
我会自己拿主意!

134
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:05,740
MAXTIBLE: Do not antagonize them, Doctor.
They will destroy your time machine!
不要激怒他们, 博士. 他们会毁了你的时间机器的!

135
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:12,450
MAXTIBLE: And if I agree, it means the creation of a race of super-Daleks!
但如果我同意, 那就意味着超级 Daleks 的诞生!

136
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:21,200
DOCTOR: My TARDIS... I have no choice, do I?
我的 TARDIS...我没有选择, 有吗?

137
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,400
DOCTOR: Very well. I agree.
好吧, 我同意了

138
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:28,710
DALEK: The human being with you must not be aware of the trial.
跟着你的那个人必须对这项实验不知情

139
00:11:29,070 --> 00:11:30,340
DOCTOR: I quite understand.
我很明白

140
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:33,160
DALEK: Make him begin the test!
让他开始实验!

141
00:11:42,900 --> 00:11:44,430
DOCTOR: What must Jamie do?
Jamie 必须干什么?

142
00:11:45,530 --> 00:11:49,840
MAXTIBLE: Attempt to rescue Waterfield's daughter.
尝试营救 Waterfield 的女儿

143
00:11:58,340 --> 00:12:00,370
- MOLLIE: There we are, sir.   - RUTH: Thank you, Mollie.
- 就是这里, 先生 - 谢谢你, Mollie

144
00:12:00,740 --> 00:12:03,060
RUTH: Arthur, I'd like you to meet Mr. McCrimmon.
Arthur, 我引你见一下 McCrimmon 先生

145
00:12:03,430 --> 00:12:05,480
TERRALL: May I ask what you are doing in this house?
我能问问你在这个房子里面干什么吗?

146
00:12:05,810 --> 00:12:07,980
JAMIE: I was just about to ask you the same thing.
我也正要问你同一个问题

147
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:09,940
RUTH: Oh, you gentlemen have been introduced?
哦, 有人已经介绍两位先生认识了?

148
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,280
JAMIE: Aye, we've met.
是, 我们见过面

149
00:12:11,950 --> 00:12:15,840
TERRALL: It seems, Ruth, your father has the
oddest collection of house guests these days.
看起来, Ruth 小姐, 你父亲这几天招待了一大堆奇怪的客人啊

150
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:18,220
RUTH: Now Arthur, please!
Arthur, 别这样

151
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,460
RUTH: You must forgive him, Mr. McCrimmon.
你得原谅他, McCrimmon 先生

152
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:21,910
JAMIE: Ah, it's becoming a habit.
啊, 都已经习惯了

153
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,440
TERRALL: I don't care for insolence.
我并不太在意这些无礼的行为

154
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:25,760
JAMIE: Well, I'm not keen on arrogance myself!
哈, 我也不太在乎那些自大的家伙

155
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:28,860
RUTH: Why, you bite at each other as if you were old enemies!
为什么, 你们俩就好像宿敌一样要互相咬?

156
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,610
JAMIE: I'm sorry if I seem rude.
如果我看起来比较无礼, 我很抱歉

157
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:35,220
RUTH: Come, I want you to be friends.
Won't you be so, to please me?
好了, 我期望你们成为朋友. 你们可以吗, 就给我点面子?

158
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:42,440
RUTH: Arthur... Arthur, what is it?
Arthur... Arthur, 怎么了?

159
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:43,860
RUTH: Excuse me.
抱歉

160
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:45,960
RUTH: Arthur! What's the matter?
Arthur! 什么情况?

161
00:12:53,190 --> 00:12:54,660
- MOLLIE: Sir?   - Yes?!
- 先生?    - 什么事?

162
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:57,760
JAMIE: Oh, I wish you'd call me Jamie.
哦, 我期望你叫我 Jamie

163
00:12:57,890 --> 00:13:00,400
MOLLIE: Oh, I couldn't do that sir. What would the master say?
噢, 我不能那样做, 先生. 不知道主人会怎么说我呢

164
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:03,410
JAMIE: Oh, who cares! Ah, What can I do for you?
哦, 谁在乎! 啊, 有什么能帮到你的?

165
00:13:03,630 --> 00:13:07,000
MOLLIE: If you'd tell me where your bags are, sir - yours and the Doctor's
如果你能告诉我你的包裹在哪儿 —— 你的和博士的

166
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,360
MOLLIE: I'll have them taken up to your room.
我会让人把他们带到你的房间来的

167
00:13:08,390 --> 00:13:09,630
JAMIE: Aye. well, Mollie...
啊, 这个, Mollie...

168
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:13,840
MOLLIE: Listen to me, "have them taken. "
I dare say I'll be doin' it meself!
听我说, 我说“让人带过来”, 其实我会亲自做的!

169
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:16,640
JAMIE: You see, we didn't have time to
pick up the luggage. It'll be following.
你看, 我们并没有时间收拾行李, 过两天才会送来

170
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:17,460
MOLLIE: Oh.
哦

171
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,740
JAMIE: Why do you say that you'll be doing it yourself?
为什么你说你要自己做?

172
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:22,790
MOLLIE: Well, they do say, sir, that the house is haunted.
哦, 他们说, 先生, 这房子闹鬼

173
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:24,380
MOLLIE: Mr. Kitson, the butler, left.
Kitson 先生, 我们的管家离开了

174
00:13:24,460 --> 00:13:26,940
MOLLIE: And cook and the two footmen are complainin' again.
厨师和两个杂役都在说这个

175
00:13:26,990 --> 00:13:30,340
- JAMIE: Haunted?  -  MOLLIE: Mmm. But, I've never heard anything sir.
- 闹鬼?    - 嗯. 不过, 我从来没听到过什么, 先生

176
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:32,580
MOLLIE: I sleep like a log and always have.
我睡觉跟一根木头似的, 总是这样

177
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,900
JAMIE: Aye. well, I'm glad you've got over the fright you had.
啊, 我很高兴你已经克服了恐惧

178
00:13:35,100 --> 00:13:38,520
JAMIE: Oh, yes, that horrible man.
噢, 是的, 那个吓人的家伙

179
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:42,500
MOLLIE: Miss Ruth said it was all a game, but I dunno sir.
Ruth 小姐说只是个游戏, 不过我也搞不懂. 

180
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:45,440
MOLLIE: I've never fainted before, sir. Truly I haven't.
我以前从来没有晕倒过, 先生. 真的没有

181
00:13:45,580 --> 00:13:48,380
JAMIE: Not "sir", "Jamie"!
不是“先生”, 叫我“Jamie”!

182
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,440
JAMIE: Tell me about Arthur Terrall.
告诉我一些 Arthur Terrall 的情况

183
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:53,360
MOLLIE: Miss Ruth's fiance, sir?
Ruth 小姐的未婚夫吗, 先生

184
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:56,860
MOLLIE: Oh, oh, he's a kind man, sir. Usually.
哦, 他是个好人, 先生. 通常来说

185
00:13:56,950 --> 00:13:58,080
JAMIE: Usually?
通常来说?

186
00:13:58,160 --> 00:14:02,200
MOLLIE: Mmm. Well, when he's a bit odd or his temper's up,
as it has been lately,
嗯, 就是, 他有点怪, 或者脾气上来了, 就像最近那样

187
00:14:02,420 --> 00:14:05,600
MOLLIE: I says to meself "Inkerman" and then it's all right.
我跟自己说, 估计“英克曼人”就是那样

188
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:07,280
- JAMIE: "Inkerman"?   - MOLLIE: Yes sir.
- “英克曼人”?   - 是的先生

189
00:14:07,420 --> 00:14:09,300
MOLLIE:  'e was out in the Crimea, 'e was.
他之前在克里米亚

190
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:12,060
MOLLIE: They do say Mr. Terrall was wounded out there.
他们的确说过 Terrall 在那里受了伤

191
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:15,260
MOLLIE: Do you know, my uncle was killed at Inkerman, sir.
你知道吗, 我叔叔就是在英克曼战死的, 先生
<i>(备注：1854-1856年, 俄国与英、法为争夺小亚细亚地区权利而爆发“克里米亚战争“)</i>

192
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:17,760
MOLLIE: So, you see, I do know what it's like with soldiers.
所以, 你看, 我还真知道士兵是怎样的
<i>(备注：1854-1856年, 俄国与英、法为争夺小亚细亚地区权利而爆发“克里米亚战争“)</i>

193
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:21,670
- MOLLIE: Oh... oh, I'm sorry sir. I didn't mean to...
- DOCTOR: Never mind. Mollie.
- 噢, 对不起先生. 我不是有意的...  - 没事的, Mollie

194
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:24,480
MOLLIE: Well cook said to me that
if I did some dusting it would be all right.
厨师跟我说, 我打扫打扫就可以了

195
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:26,140
MOLLIE: Oh, you won't tell the master, will you?
哦, 你不会告诉主人的, 是吗?

196
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:28,170
- DOCTOR: I wouldn't dream of telling him.
- MOLLIE: Thank you. Sorry sir.
- 我不会告诉他的  - 谢谢你, 对不起,先生

197
00:14:28,220 --> 00:14:30,300
DOCTOR: Thank you very much, Bye-bye.
很谢谢你, 拜拜

198
00:14:32,570 --> 00:14:34,800
DOCTOR: Hmm, you'll have to brush up on your history.
你得刷新一下你的历史知识了

199
00:14:34,860 --> 00:14:38,060
DOCTOR: I can't be around to cover up for you all the time.
我不可能总在你身边帮你补课
<i>(备注: Jamie 是172x年诞生的, 174x年开始跟随博士旅行, 所以他对后面的历史知道得不多)</i>

200
00:14:38,220 --> 00:14:43,400
DOCTOR: Now then, in the Crimean War, the English, the French
and the Turks fought the Russians...
这一次, 克里米亚战争, 英国人、法国人和土耳其人一起跟俄国人打

201
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:45,840
- JAMIE: Oh, forget about all that!
- DOCTOR: Oh, I thought you'd be interested.
- 哦, 忘了那些吧  - 哦, 我还以为你感兴趣

202
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:50,200
DOCTOR: I watched the Charge of the Light Brigade. Magnificent folly...
我可见过轻骑兵发起的冲锋, 那可真是愚蠢...
<i>(备注: 此处特指1854年10月克里米亚战争巴拉克拉瓦战役中,
英国轻骑兵向俄军发起的冲锋, 因命令传达错误而伤亡惨重. 
因诗歌 The Charge of the Light Brigade 而受后人铭记)</i>

203
00:14:50,260 --> 00:14:51,400
DOCTOR: Look, where've you been?
我说, 你都去哪儿了?

204
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,520
DOCTOR: Oh, just looking around.
哦, 只是四处看看

205
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,180
JAMIE: Aye. What for? The TARDIS?!
啊, 看什么? TARDIS 吗?

206
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:57,420
DOCTOR: Jamie, you're in a temper!
Jamie, 你在闹脾气啊

207
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:59,600
JAMIE: Oh, am I? Is that bad then?
哦, 是吗? 这很糟糕吧?

208
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:01,300
JAMIE: Does that mean I won't be co-operative
是不是意味着我不会乖乖听话了?

209
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:03,380
- JAMIE: I won't do everything I'm told?   - DOCTOR: What was that?
- 不会说什么我就做什么了?  - 这是怎么了?

210
00:15:03,460 --> 00:15:05,140
JAMIE: I overheard you and Waterfield!
我听到了你和 Waterfield 的对话!

211
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:07,600
- DOCTOR: You were eavesdropping!
-JAMIE: Well, whatever it is, I don't like what you're doing.
- 你居然在偷听!   - 不管怎样, 我不喜欢你现在做的事

212
00:15:07,660 --> 00:15:08,760
- DOCTOR: Now you listen to me...!   - JAMIE: No, Doctor,
- 你听我说...!   - 不了, 博士

213
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:11,480
JAMIE: You're forgetting the TARDIS was stolen and a man was murdered!
你已经忘记 TARDIS 被偷了, 还有人被杀了

214
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:14,580
JAMIE: Now, how am I supposed to tell when I see
you as friendly as you like with the murderer!
现在, 我看见你跟杀人凶手在一起跟朋友似的, 你让我怎么想呢?

215
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:16,720
DOCTOR: Waterfield did not murder that man!
Waterfield 没有杀那个人!

216
00:15:16,780 --> 00:15:19,290
JAMIE: All right then, but he stole the TARDIS
and that still makes him a thief!
那好, 但他偷了 TARDIS, 他仍然还是一个小偷!

217
00:15:19,450 --> 00:15:21,940
- DOCTOR: The Daleks forced him to!
- The Daleks! You keep telling me about the Daleks,
- Daleks 强迫他干的!   - Daleks!  你一直跟我说 Daleks

218
00:15:21,980 --> 00:15:23,140
JAMIE: and I haven't even seen one!
但我一个没见着!

219
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:24,920
JAMIE: You're always on about them, but where are they?!
你总叨叨他们, 但他们在哪儿呢?

220
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:27,720
- DOCTOR: Now you listen to me...!
- JAMIE: No, you'll not get round me this time, Doctor.
- 你听我说!  - 不, 这次你别想忽悠我了, 博士

221
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:29,620
JAMIE: You're up to something with Waterfield and Maxtible.
你跟 Waterfield 还有 Maxtible 在搞些什么

222
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:32,680
JAMIE: Now what is it? Some scientific invention?!
到底是什么呢? 某种科学发明吗? !

223
00:15:33,010 --> 00:15:34,520
JAMIE: Ah, here's your friend.
啊, 你的朋友来了

224
00:15:34,580 --> 00:15:35,760
DOCTOR: Just a little argument.
只是一点小争论

225
00:15:35,860 --> 00:15:37,580
WATERFIELD: I heard voices raised.
我听着声音有点大了

226
00:15:37,660 --> 00:15:38,590
JAMIE: That's not all you'll hear!
你能听见的才不止这点呢

227
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:40,860
DOCTOR: Jamie seems to think that I'm lying to him.
Jamie 似乎认为我在欺骗他

228
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:41,960
JAMIE: Well, aren't you?!
怎么, 没有吗?

229
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:43,800
DOCTOR: He doesn't believe the Daleks are here.
他并不相信 Daleks 就在这里

230
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:44,660
WATERFIELD: It's the truth.
这是事实

231
00:15:44,770 --> 00:15:46,860
JAMIE: Aye, the truth you told Arthur Terrall, maybe
对, 事实, 你告诉 Arthur Terrall 的也是事实

232
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:49,620
- JAMIE: that your daughter was in Paris!
- WATERFIELD: I had to tell him that.
- 说你的女儿在巴黎!   - 我只能那样跟他说

233
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:51,400
JAMIE: So, you've got another story to tell me?
所以你还有另外一个故事是给我的罗?

234
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:54,480
WATERFIELD: I tell you that the Daleks are holding my daughter prisoner
我跟你说, 我女儿现在就囚禁着我女儿

235
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:56,220
WATERFIELD: in the south wing of this house, Mr. McCrimmon.
就在这栋房子的南面, McCrimmon 先生

236
00:15:56,300 --> 00:15:59,320
JAMIE: Then why don't you try and get her back, eh?!
What are you doing?!
那你怎么不试着把她救回来, 嗯? 你在忙些什么?

237
00:15:59,380 --> 00:16:01,780
DOCTOR: Well, what can I do? Now, be... be fair Jamie.
我能怎么做? 你看...得讲点道理啊 Jamie

238
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:04,420
DOCTOR: Waterfield's tied hand and foot because of his daughter
Waterfield 因为他女儿而投鼠忌器

239
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:06,440
DOCTOR: and we're tied hand and foot because of the TARDIS!
而我们因为 TARDIS 而束手束脚

240
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:08,750
JAMIE: Aye, and that's all you can
think about, isn't it? The TARDIS?
啊, 你能想到的就只有这个, TARDIS, 是吗?

241
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:11,750
JAMIE: Well, you can all stand around doing nothing.
I'm sick to death of it!
你就站在那里什么也不做? 我恶心死了!

242
00:16:11,870 --> 00:16:13,000
DOCTOR: Now just where are you going?
你现在要去哪儿?

243
00:16:13,140 --> 00:16:15,390
JAMIE: To be by myself for a bit. Do you mind?
一个人呆一会儿, 你管得着吗?

244
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:17,800
DOCTOR: No, not a bit. But, one word of warning.
不, 管不着. 但警告你一句话

245
00:16:18,040 --> 00:16:21,080
DOCTOR: Don't you try to be a one-man army. You leave well alone.
别想一个人逞英雄. 你别管这事

246
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:24,960
DOCTOR: I won't have you ruining everything
trying to rescue Victoria Waterfield.
我不能允许你为了救 Victoria Waterfield 而毁了一切

247
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,420
DOCTOR: Now, you understand?!
你听明白了没有? !

248
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:33,370
WATERFIELD: Well, are you sure you didn't go a little too far, Doctor?
唉, 你确定这样是不是有点过火了, 博士?

249
00:16:33,770 --> 00:16:36,380
DOCTOR: Adding a little fuel to the fire.
我给火上浇点油

250
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:40,320
DOCTOR: Tell Maxtible that I'll be along to his laboratory shortly.
告诉 Maxtible 我很快就到他的实验室去

251
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:42,620
- WATERFIELD: Oh, very well, Doctor. If you're sure.
- DOCTOR: Oh yes, quite sure.
- 好吧, 博士, 如果你确定的话  - 是的, 很确定

252
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:46,600
DOCTOR: Once our young friend has cooled
his heels a bit, he'll launch off on his own.
一旦我们的小朋友冷静一点, 他就会自己开始行动了

253
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:50,100
DOCTOR: And you dropped the hint about the south wing beautifully.
而且你也很漂亮地把南厢房的线索传递给他了

254
00:16:56,960 --> 00:17:00,820
TERRALL: Well, what is it?
怎么, 什么事?

255
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:03,580
TERRALL: You wanted to see me?
你想要见我?

256
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:07,600
- TOBY: Very good of you to talk to me, gov'nor.
- TERRALL: Well, never mind all that.
- 你愿意跟我谈谈太好了, 先生  - 得, 别来这些了

257
00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:09,600
TERRALL: I'll give you two minutes, no more.
我给你两分钟, 多了没有

258
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:11,500
TOBY: I want me rights. No more, no less.
我想争取我的权利, 不多要, 也不能少给

259
00:17:11,650 --> 00:17:13,090
TERRALL: What do you mean, "rights"?
你什么意思, “权利”?

260
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:15,470
TOBY: 'alf a guinea, you gave me, and it ain't what we said.
你就给了半个基尼, 这不是我们之前说好的

261
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,680
TERRALL: You were lucky to get anything.
你还能拿到一点就不错了

262
00:17:18,190 --> 00:17:20,460
- TOBY: That ain't fair!  - TERRALL: You'll get no more from me.
- 这不公平  - 你别想从我这里得到更多钱

263
00:17:20,860 --> 00:17:23,540
TERRALL: I warn you! Keep away from
this house, and this property.
我警告你, 离这个房子远点儿

264
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:26,140
TERRALL: Find the nearest road to London and take it!
找到去伦敦的路, 走吧

265
00:17:27,120 --> 00:17:28,323
TOBY: Oh, yeah, London, sir. Yeah.
哦, 好啊, 伦敦, 先生, 成

266
00:17:28,423 --> 00:17:31,920
TOBY: I daresay I could earn something for me stories there.
我敢说, 到了那里我只凭讲故事就可以挣到钱啦

267
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:35,460
- TERRALL: Stories?
- TOBY: Oh, I won't detain an important gentleman like yourself.
- 故事?   - 我可不敢再耽误您这样的绅士了

268
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:37,870
TOBY: Like as not me two minutes is up anyway.
似乎我的两分钟已经到了

269
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:39,280
TERRALL: What do you mean, "stories"?
你什么意思, “讲故事”?

270
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:41,180
TOBY: Ah, it's all right, sir. I'll take a stroll to London...
啊, 没事, 先生. 我得上路去伦敦了. . . 

271
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:42,670
TERRALL: Don't play with me!
别跟我玩花样!

272
00:17:42,910 --> 00:17:44,745
TOBY: Get off me!
离我远点

273
00:17:45,845 --> 00:17:48,580
TOBY: If you must know, there's plenty
who'd pay to hear what I've got to tell 'em.
如果你非得知道, 有好多人愿意付钱听我给他们讲呢

274
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:49,610
TERRALL: Indeed?
真的?

275
00:17:49,810 --> 00:17:52,444
TOBY: Yeah. You blows too hot and cold for me
是啊, 你这一会儿阴一会儿晴

276
00:17:52,544 --> 00:17:54,880
- tellin' me this one minute and that the next, and not payin' up.
一会儿跟我这么说, 一会儿又那么说, 还不付钱

277
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:56,120
TERRALL: You know nothing.
你什么也不知道

278
00:17:56,460 --> 00:17:57,960
TOBY: Don't I though?
我不知道吗?

279
00:17:58,470 --> 00:17:59,940
TERRALL: Hmm. Who'd believe you anyway?
唔, 谁会信你呢?

280
00:18:00,100 --> 00:18:01,780
TOBY: Pay me off, and there's the end of it!
把钱付了, 这事儿就算完了

281
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:04,660
TERRALL: Oh, blackmail is it?! Get out!
噢, 勒索是吗?  滚出去!

282
00:18:29,130 --> 00:18:30,880
TOBY: Maybe I don't know much to tell,
也许我知道得不多

283
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:34,620
TOBY: but I'll wager I'll find something
in the house that's worth me trouble.
但我打赌我能在这房子里找到点什么, 肯定有料

284
00:18:34,980 --> 00:18:37,330
TOBY: So, I'll say thank ya, Mr. Terrall, sir!
那, 我就说声谢谢你了, Terrall 先生

285
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,100
JAMIE: It's only me, Mollie!
是我, Mollie!

286
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:15,700
MOLLIE: It's over here, sir. I took it from the master's study.
在这里了, 先生. 我从主人的书房里面拿出来的

287
00:19:15,820 --> 00:19:17,550
JAMIE: It's marvellous. Thank you!
这太棒了, 谢谢你!

288
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:20,460
MOLLIE: 'ere, is this what you wanted?
这里, 这是你想要的吗?

289
00:19:22,430 --> 00:19:25,560
JAMIE: Perfect, yes. Let's see, umm...
非常好, 好了, 让我来看看, 唔...

290
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:28,840
- JAMIE: This is the south wing here?   - MOLLIE: Yes, sir.
- 这里是南厢房吗?   - 是的, 先生

291
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:31,100
- MOLLIE: But it's been closed off.   - JAMIE: Completely?
- 但它被封起来了 - 完全封了?

292
00:19:31,180 --> 00:19:33,940
MOLLIE: Oh, no sir. Only 'cause of some repairs
about a twelve-month back.
哦, 不是, 先生. 只是一些修缮工作, 都快一年了

293
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:35,840
MOLLIE: But the door may be locked.
不过门可能被锁住了

294
00:19:36,020 --> 00:19:37,740
- JAMIE: Can you show me?  - MOLLIE: All right.
- 你能指给我看一下吗?   - 好吧

295
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:44,380
MOLLIE: What're you gonna do, sir?
你打算做什么, 先生?

296
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:46,540
JAMIE: Off to hunt a few wee ghosties, Mollie.
去抓几个小鬼, Mollie

297
00:19:49,180 --> 00:19:55,780
DOCTOR: Every single one of Jamie's reactions
will be recorded on these Dalek machines?
而 Jamie 的每个动作都会在 Dalek 的这些机器上记录下来?

298
00:19:55,940 --> 00:20:01,580
MAXTIBLE: And then transformed into thought patterns
on silver wire. A wonderful creation!
然后再转化成思维模型, 存储到银线. 多么漂亮的发明!

299
00:20:01,850 --> 00:20:08,680
DALEK: It is for you, Doctor, to select the major feelings
to make up this "human factor".
然后要由博士你, 负责挑选出那些组成“人类特质”的主要情感

300
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:10,220
DOCTOR: Oh, yes. I quite understand.
哦, 是的, 我完全明白

301
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:13,540
MAXTIBLE: We can rely on the Doctor to give us all cooperation.
我们可以信赖博士给予我们全面的合作

302
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:16,370
DALEK: We shall watch your every move.
我们会盯着你的一举一动

303
00:20:16,700 --> 00:20:17,960
DOCTOR: I'm sure you will.
我确信你们会的

304
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:22,140
DOCTOR: And every step of Jamie's progress will be covered?
Jamie 的每一步也会包含在内吧?

305
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,600
DALEK: Yes.
是的

306
00:20:25,460 --> 00:20:29,120
DALEK: The young human being is on his way.
那个年轻的人类已经在路上了

307
00:20:29,410 --> 00:20:31,940
DOCTOR: Then the recording machines can be set in action.
那么录制设备就可以开启了

308
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,880
- JAMIE: Here!   - MOLLIE: Yes, sir.
- 这里  - 是的, 先生

309
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:41,260
MOLLIE: I once remember the master stepping away from here.
我记得有一次主人就从这里走过去的

310
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:44,000
MOLLIE: When he saw me, he was very cross and told me to keep away.
他看见我的时候非常生气, 让我离开

311
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,020
JAMIE: I see.
我明白了

312
00:21:28,980 --> 00:21:31,180
MOLLIE: What was that? What was that?!
什么声音? 那是什么声音?

313
00:21:31,320 --> 00:21:33,200
JAMIE: That was no ghost, Mollie, that's for sure.
那不是鬼, Mollie, 这点可以肯定

314
00:21:33,340 --> 00:21:35,860
- JAMIE: That was a human voice!   - MOLLIE: Oh, sir!
- 那是一个人的声音!   - 哦, 先生!

315
00:21:35,940 --> 00:21:38,320
JAMIE: Look Mollie, take the candle and go back to your room.
Mollie, 拿着蜡烛, 回到你的房间去

316
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:39,480
- JAMIE: Will you do that?  - MOLLIE: Yes sir.
- 你可以吗?  - 可以先生

317
00:21:39,580 --> 00:21:40,820
JAMIE: Now, do you want me to see you safely there?
你期望我陪你过去, 以确保你安全到达吗?

318
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:43,310
MOLLIE: No, no. I'll be all right.
不, 不用, 我没事的

319
00:22:55,300 --> 00:22:58,240
Hello. Who are you?
JAMIE: 你好, 你是谁?

